### SkyManager API - Endpoints

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/

### ==================== FLIGHTS ====================

### Listar todos los vuelos
GET http://localhost:3000/flights

### Obtener vuelo por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/flights/00de318f-262b-4958-bd59-50cfc2db432c

### Crear vuelo
POST http://localhost:3000/flights
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "origin": "MEX",
  "destination": "SAL",
  "airline_id": "81eadc87-af17-45fd-9242-69a13120a815",
  "departure_time": "2026-08-01T08:00:00Z",
  "arrival_time": "2026-08-01T09:00:00Z",
  "status": "scheduled",
  "gate": "D4",
  "capacity": 150
}

### Actualizar vuelo
PUT http://localhost:3000/flights/00de318f-262b-4958-bd59-50cfc2db432c
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "departed",
  "gate": "D4"
}

### Eliminar vuelo
DELETE http://localhost:3000/flights/00de318f-262b-4958-bd59-50cfc2db432c

### ==================== AIRLINES ====================

### Listar todas las aerolíneas
GET http://localhost:3000/airlines

### Obtener aerolínea por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/airlines/81eadc87-af17-45fd-9242-69a13120a815

### Crear aerolínea
POST http://localhost:3000/airlines
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Copa Airlines",
  "iata_code": "CM",
  "country": "Panama",
  "logo_url": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/c2/Copa_Airlines_logo.svg"
}

### Actualizar aerolínea
PUT http://localhost:3000/airlines/81eadc87-af17-45fd-9242-69a13120a815
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "country": "Honduras"
}

### Eliminar aerolínea
DELETE http://localhost:3000/airlines/b44e1699-499e-44c6-bb44-0b0d79a1058f

### ==================== AIRPORTS ====================

### Listar todos los aeropuertos
GET http://localhost:3000/airports

### Obtener aeropuerto por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/airports/fbfe3b69-f2bb-4087-8269-1a8fe83bfc05

### Crear aeropuerto
POST http://localhost:3000/airports
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "iata_code": "BOG",
  "name": "Aeropuerto Internacional El Dorado",
  "city": "Bogota",
  "country": "Colombia"
}

### Actualizar aeropuerto
PUT http://localhost:3000/airports/15101a50-3d46-47b1-9458-9e8683cc6d43
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "city": "Roatan, Islas de la Bahia"
}

### Eliminar aeropuerto
DELETE http://localhost:3000/airports/15101a50-3d46-47b1-9458-9e8683cc6d43

### ==================== PASSENGERS ====================

### Listar todos los pasajeros
GET http://localhost:3000/passengers

### Obtener pasajero por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/passengers/00932999-7993-44d4-a146-92ee994ed5a1

### Crear pasajero
POST http://localhost:3000/passengers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Maria",
  "last_name": "Gonzalez",
  "passport": "GT99887766",
  "nationality": "Guatemala",
  "email": "maria.gonzalez@email.com"
}

### Actualizar pasajero
PUT http://localhost:3000/passengers/8db424d4-c97c-4ec4-8b27-6eb7a87a2002
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ana.martinez.nuevo@email.com"
}

### Eliminar pasajero
DELETE http://localhost:3000/passengers/8db424d4-c97c-4ec4-8b27-6eb7a87a2002

### ==================== BOOKINGS ====================

### Listar todas las reservas
GET http://localhost:3000/bookings

### Obtener reserva por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/bookings/7e4da702-5389-4812-ba27-ca7de40d4006

### Crear reserva (exitosa)
POST http://localhost:3000/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "passenger_id": "8db424d4-c97c-4ec4-8b27-6eb7a87a2002",
  "flight_id": "00de318f-262b-4958-bd59-50cfc2db432c",
  "seat_number": "14C",
  "booking_date": "2026-07-16T10:00:00Z",
  "status": "confirmed"
}

### Crear reserva (pasajero inexistente - debe dar 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "passenger_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "flight_id": "00de318f-262b-4958-bd59-50cfc2db432c",
  "seat_number": "15A",
  "booking_date": "2026-07-16T10:00:00Z",
  "status": "confirmed"
}

### Crear reserva (asiento ocupado - debe dar 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "passenger_id": "8db424d4-c97c-4ec4-8b27-6eb7a87a2002",
  "flight_id": "00de318f-262b-4958-bd59-50cfc2db432c",
  "seat_number": "12A",
  "booking_date": "2026-07-16T10:00:00Z",
  "status": "confirmed"
}

### Actualizar reserva
PUT http://localhost:3000/bookings/7e4da702-5389-4812-ba27-ca7de40d4006
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "cancelled"
}

### Eliminar reserva
DELETE http://localhost:3000/bookings/abbe24fd-8e0e-45df-89bc-da46191879ee
